To the Editor:

Re ''Movie Stars Onstage: Big Daddy Speaks Out''' (Arts pages, Nov. 25):

Ned Beatty's withering assessment of the acting ability of his ''Cat on a Hot Tin Roof'' co-stars was unseemly and ungracious. I was relieved to read he is considering retirement, lest I someday find myself on the same bill.

DAVID D. TURNER

New York, Nov. 26, 2003

The writer is an actor.